      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a rough-running engine and a transmission that hesitates between gears. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust on the rocker panels and several large dents. The interior requires a deep cleaning and has multiple tears in the upholstery. This car is best suited for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a major project or as a donor vehicle for parts.",
