    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project? This car is a fantastic candidate for someone who loves to roll up their sleeves and bring a vehicle back to life! While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a great foundation for a restoration or a dedicated parts vehicle. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own!",
