      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of uncompromising quality. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior appointments, reflects a commitment to excellence. For the discerning buyer, this represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in a truly peerless state.",
      "price": 46500.0,
